<div class="container">
    <h1>📋 SKR PROCEDURE — Safe Keeping Receipt (Gold)</h1>
    <p>Buy SKR with EURX or monetize SKR for a loan.</p>

    <div class="note">
        <p>💰 <strong>EURX Price:</strong> 1 EURX = 1 евро (1:1)</p>
        <p>🏦 <strong>BYT Price (for collateral):</strong> 1 BYT = $227,273,174</p>
    </div>

    <h2>🔐 STEP 1 — CIP & Video KYC (Mandatory)</h2>
    <p><strong>For companies:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Certificate of Incorporation</li>
        <li>Memorandum & Articles of Association</li>
        <li>Register of Directors / Shareholders</li>
        <li>Ultimate Beneficial Ownership (UBO) structure</li>
        <li>Proof of business address</li>
        <li>Audited financials (if available)</li>
        <li>Corporate bank account statement</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>For individuals:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Passport (color copy, all pages)</li>
        <li>Proof of residence (utility bill, bank statement)</li>
        <li>Source of funds declaration</li>
        <li>Bank reference letter (if available)</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>📹 Video KYC (Live Session):</strong> 15–20 min video call, show original passport, confirm identity, sign documents digitally.</p>

    <h2>🔒 STEP 2 — EURX Blocked in Escrow</h2>
    <p>We block EURX in escrow (90 days until SKR verified). Escrow provider: LEXR / Escrow.com / BNY Mellon</p>

    <h2>🏦 STEP 3 — SKR Transfer via SWIFT</h2>
    <p>You transfer SKR to our escrow using MT 599 (free format) or MX (ISO 20022) — camt.106 / camt.105</p>
    <p><strong>HSBC SWIFT:</strong> BLIC GB2L | <strong>Telex:</strong> 889217 RNB</p>

    <h2>✅ STEP 4 — Verification & Execution</h2>
    <p>We verify SKR authenticity, ownership chain, gold purity & quantity. After verification: EURX released to you (purchase) or loan sent via SWIFT (monetization).</p>

    <h2>🏦 Monetize SKR — Loan Against Gold</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>You provide SKR (gold in bank vault)</li>
        <li>We block EURX in escrow (same value as loan)</li>
        <li>Bank issues loan against SKR (up to 70% of gold value)</li>
        <li>Loan funds sent via SWIFT to your bank account</li>
        <li>After loan confirmation → we release EURX to you</li>
    </ul>

